		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[Dear Dr. Schulze,

Doctor! hope all is well.

Thanks to my Pastor for giving me your video information, and after 25+ hours of studying your videos and taking alot of notes, etc. i have a question. 

Before hand, just want to say thank you! Doctors give no hope when it comes to cancer. i'm writing in regards to my father. on march 20th 2014, they found a 9cm tumor in his recktom, and had mets to liver and lymph node. all of the founding were all early and the mets very small. they said 6m-2yrs with Chemo.

