he has lost 25-30 pounds. looks so healthy and feels really strong. he is alittle skinner in appearance(family is scared, but i know he is good). he also has his appetite very well.

my question is- at times he poops like a mucus with small portion of blood! is that because of the cleansing?? and when he poops his lower back hurts just a little, not a serious pain(only when finishes pooping).

we will continue to go strong!! and i will continue to follow your steps!!!

