		<title> Fasting Facts</title>
		<link>http://dev.emizentech.com/herbdocblog/?post_type=Question&#038;p=17799</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 30 Nov -0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dr. Schulze]]></dc:creator>
		
		<category domain="status" nicename="saved"><![CDATA[Saved]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://herbdocblog.com/?post_type=Question&#038;p=17799</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Dear]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_id>17799</wp:post_id>
		<wp:post_date>2014-06-06 13:33:25</wp:post_date>
		<wp:post_date_gmt>0000-00-00 00:00:00</wp:post_date_gmt>
		<wp:comment_status>closed</wp:comment_status>
		<wp:ping_status>closed</wp:ping_status>
		<wp:post_name></wp:post_name>
		<wp:status>draft</wp:status>
		<wp:post_parent>0</wp:post_parent>
		<wp:menu_order>0</wp:menu_order>
		<wp:post_type>Question</wp:post_type>
		<wp:post_password></wp:post_password>
		<wp:is_sticky>0</wp:is_sticky>
								<wp:postmeta>
		<wp:meta_key>mf_post_question</wp:meta_key>
		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[Dear Dr. Schulze,

Just wanted to share that science has confirmed what you've been telling us for years: Fasting heals the body when it's compromised by disease. 

I know that I feel better after a 5-day or more juice fast! Here's the proof in the pudding, or rather proof in fasting:

This is an excerpt from an article in the Daily Mail:
"Fasting for as little as three days can regenerate the entire immune system, even in the elderly, scientists have found in a breakthrough described as 'remarkable'.
Although fasting diets have been criticised by nutritionists for being unhealthy, new research suggests starving the body kick-starts stem cells into producing new white blood cells, which fight off infection.
The researchers say fasting 'flips a regenerative switch' which prompts stem cells to create brand new white blood cells, essentially regenerating the entire immune system."

http://www.dailymail.co.uk/health/article-2650456/Fasting-just-eight-days-year-boost-immune-new-study-finds.html#ixzz33sMP2tcx 

And here's an excerpt from an article in the National Post:
"Scientists at the University of Southern California (USC) say the discovery could be particularly beneficial for those suffering from damaged immune systems, such as cancer patients on chemotherapy."

Professor Valter Longo at the university said, "There is no evidence at all that fasting would be dangerous while there is strong evidence that it is beneficial. Fasting cycles can generate, literally, a new immune system."

http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/06/05/fasting-for-three-days-renews-entire-immune-system-protects-cancer-patients-remarkable-new-study-finds/

Pretty amazing stuff!

Best, 
D.R., Saratoga, NY]]></wp:meta_value>
