		<wp:is_sticky>0</wp:is_sticky>
								<wp:postmeta>
		<wp:meta_key>mf_post_question</wp:meta_key>
		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[Dear Dr. Schulze,
is there a way to dissolve arterial plaques that have built up over the years using herbal methods?  i am 63, walk 1 hr daily, non-smoker, and I have become vegan+organic eggs over last 4 years and am very careful with diet and drink only veg. juices and purified water. 

but i seem to have a stubborn high blood pressure which does not seem to be getting better with time. i take only 1 med. for BP, valsartin.

i am getting a bit discouraged about being able to handle this in an organized way. i am now increasing Sun light to about 20min daily having read increasing vit. D helps w/BP but past this i am stumped about how to take more responsibility for my vascular health.  

