Immediately we stopped giving her any cereal and started adding homemade baby food to her bottles, the next week I started making her a home made meat based baby formula and each bottle included formula, fruit or vegetable puree, and 1/8 tsp of your superfood. Within a couple of weeks she started having regular soft bowel movements twice a day!! What a wonderful thing! She started gaining weight and is now 14 lbs! She can babble to us, play peek a boo, smiles all the time, crawls, rolls over, stands on her own, eats from a spoon, eats finger foods, give kisses, and loves to be active and play. She has had 6 months worth of progress in 2 months!!
The problems I am still concerned about are her optical nerve being small, I'm not sure if her kidney is still swollen, she still has dark circles under her eyes often, and of course we are worried about how much brain damage was done from the alcohol consumption. She is an absolute joy that we have waited waited 8 years for the Lord to bring to us!! We want the best for her and I know that you can help us repair her little body from the damage done! Thank you and I pray to get a response from you, this is incredibly important to us!]]></wp:meta_value>
