I know you advocate for strong possitive attitude and want you to know that I know I may sound "wimpy" but I really did have strong attitude which I believe has helped me all these years however, I am getting tired and my body is starting to feel the effects of years of fighting this disease.  I think you do wonderful things for many people and just wanted to thank you again for your time and consideration.  For some reason I felt compelled to reach out to you too...Hope you'll be able to respond.  God Bless...
