HELP! They are affecting my jaw (clicking) and are in the way of facial and neck movements, and sometimes they are sore. I am an actor and they are affecting my work.
I know that if I could turn the clock back and be able to come to your office that you could help me. But I also know I can't do that, nor see you! So I am hoping that you will be able to tell me what I can do. I would be forever grateful. Well, I already am grateful to you, but I'd be even more so! :-)
