I have always appreciated your mentioning the treatment of animals and pets, how your products work for them too, and I'd like to know what you would recommend for our little guy here!!! Since they eat protein, it didn't seem he should be a vegan, and I know you "fixed" your own heart!!!!!!!! This little kitty loves life, everyone says how sweet he is (and he is!), and I would like to heal his heart, Dr. Schulze. (Dehydrating the fluid out of his body and sucking fluid off is obviously not a fix.)

