I am alot better than I was, I am now walking again, alot of the CNS symptoms have gone, and I am no longer catching every cold or other illness that is going around, and no longer use iron supplements for energy.

I know that you would never have fallen into the trap of taking a fluoroquinolone, but if you were given one in say an emergency car-crash type of situation, what would you do? Is there anything more that can be done to detox?

