So, back to the current problem, how many times would you repeat the 30-day program? And is there anything else you would add to it to spice it up?

I am currently following Dr Christopher's advice for curing heavy bleeding, and it is helping, but it is a slow process.

Thanks for taking the time to answer. I know there are many thousands of others out there who are suffering from these antibiotics too.

And thanks for giving to us all so many valuable resources and information for taking our health into our own hands.

Renee]]></wp:meta_value>
