		<item>
		<title>Overweight and Diseased</title>
		<link>http://dev.emizentech.com/herbdocblog/Question/askdr-22/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 15 Aug 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dr. Schulze]]></dc:creator>
		
		<category domain="byherb" nicename="intestinal-formula-3"><![CDATA[Intestinal Formula #3]]></category>

		<category domain="bydisease" nicename="obesity"><![CDATA[Obesity]]></category>

		<category domain="bycat" nicename="natural-healing"><![CDATA[Natural Healing]]></category>

		<category domain="bycat" nicename="weight-loss"><![CDATA[Weight Loss]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://herbdocblog.com/?p=22</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Dear Tom,</p>
<p>If you are grossly overweight, very unhealthy, have all of these high<!--more--> blood values, drink, smoke, don’t exercise and have already had one heart attack, well, statistically you are in very dangerous territory, my friend. Your daughter made you write me because she obviously cares more about you being alive and living longer than you do. The question is what do you want?
</p><p>
Look my friend, I never judge, and you have as much right to live your life your way as I do to live my life my way. But in my clinic, I would call patients like you “Ticking Time Bombs” simply because you are in severe and immediate danger of having a heart attack or stroke and dying. If you are going to do something, YOU NEED TO DO IT RIGHT NOW!
</p><p>
The bottom line is, do you want to suffer through one or two more sickly years (or weeks) living your lifestyle as a fat, whining, out-of-breath pig? Or do you want to live 10, 20 or even more years to enjoy a new type of life filled with energy, vitality and gusto? It is never too late to change, my friend! I had patients fatter and in worse shape than you turn it all around, heal their heart disease, get very healthy and live on for decades.
</p><p>
I have always found that people like you—those who live life with so much gusto that they practically wind up killing themselves—when they set their mind on healing themselves and creating powerful health, they become my best patients. 
</p><p>
The question remains: Do you have the desire to live more decades instead of more months? If you chose decades, I have no doubt that you will be one of my next Natural Healing crusaders! If you would just take half of the intensity, dedication, focus and commitment that you have used to kill yourself, to now get yourself well, you will find it an easy journey, my friend. It is up to you.
</p><p>
If you choose to make this change, send me another e-mail in a few months to let me know how you are doing.
</p>
<p>– Dr. Schulze</p>]]></content:encoded>
