<p>I have 3 stents in my arteries. After my last stress test, my doctor said she did not like the amount of blood flowing out of my heart. (Ed. Note: it is possible Dale meant flowing <span style='text-decoration: underline;'>into</span> my heart via the coronary arteries.) My doctor said I might get by with another stent, but most likely I will need heart surgery. I do not want to have heart surgery. After my doctor said that, I ordered the Heart formula, Cayenne and SuperFood. Is there any other advice you would give? Thank you.</p>
<p>— Dale A.</p>]]></wp:meta_value>
