		<wp:meta_key>mf_post_question</wp:meta_key>
		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[Dear Dr. Schulze,</p>
<p>I am your biggest fan. I have healed all of my lifelong diseases and illnesses over the past decade using your herbal formulas. YOU ARE THE MAN! I have also helped most of my relatives and friends recover from their chronic problems so thank you, thank you, thank you!
</p><p>
I have one problem left, and it is not a disease, but it is my husband. No matter what, we cannot get along. He is not healthy at all, and not interested in health as I am. He ridicules me all of the time about the way I eat and my healthy lifestyle and SuperFood drinks. He has many physical problems, and even though he has gotten a lot worse over the past decade, while I have got better, he still thinks that I am the crazy one. And he loves his doctor even though he is getting sicker and sicker. I could live with that, but he is constantly making fun of my health program and he hates anything healthy, food, exercise whatever, he hates my juicer and I think he now hates me.
</p><p>
I have taken the vows of marriage, for better or for worse, so do you have any suggestions to help me heal the last problem I have? I also believe in unconditional love, so I feel that my marriage is a failure.
</p>
What herbal formulas would you suggest and I will sneak them in his food. I am very desperate as I feel that his negativity might eventually make me sick again.]]></wp:meta_value>
