		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style=''>Dear
  Joe,</span></p>
<p><span style=''>I
  want you to know how much I appreciate your letter. For me, I never get tired
  of evangelizing the power of Natural Healing and Herbal Medicine, and I NEVER
  get tired of getting letters like yours with miracles testimonies. I have seen
