		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[Dear Dr. Schulze,

I have been plagued with bouts of Conjunctivitis and Eye Irritations and Infections most of my adult life. I manage a mill, which is a very dusty and dirty environment. My doctor says it’s caused by a combination of this dirty environment plus a deformity in my tear ducts. Anyway, I seem to have an eye infection most of the time, and have been on medication and drops and creams for years, that don’t seem to have done me any good.

